{"tid":2058491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我見到同一樣嘢","createTime":"2020-06-10T08:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T08:05:08.000Z","uid":164489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0744675edc60a5ca845354d70f37720c0ac4a283","tid":2058491,"uid":164489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"話說正苦派一萬蚊，我諗住上網睇下點樣攞最快。<br />\n結果一入到條拎見到隻蜜蜂就諗起柒婆個閪樣。 <br />\n心諗條臭閪係咪咁撚痴線，連個logo都要擺自己個樣落去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cashpayout.gov.hk/chi/timetable.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cashpayout.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Ftimetable.html&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVaylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=1cc3f670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cashpayout.gov.hk/chi/timetable.html</a><br />\n<br />\nP.s 合資格既就記住攞 點用都好都咪撚益班仆街鳩官"},{"pid":"7a59f6c125d48c48f7e229e919fa1c67a7289e84","tid":2058491,"uid":136913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}